{
  "chapter": 73,
  "chapter_summary": "寇仲与徐子陵返回江阴城，遇旧友桂锡良被雨竹堂香主白荣欺压。二人出手击退白荣等雨竹堂弟子，展现精进武艺。桂锡良引二人至军师府，却被军师邵令周首徒麦云飞阻拦在外。寇仲与徐子陵在河畔闲坐，议论竹花帮内权力争斗，寇仲暗中谋划扶植桂锡良夺取帮主之位。麦云飞再次前来寻衅，被寇仲一刀震退。此时宋家小姐宋玉致率骑队经过，认出寇徐二人，劝他们离开江阴以免招惹麻烦。寇仲以魅力化解僵局，宋玉致心乱之下未加阻拦。二人在僻巷商议去留，最终决定趁夜前往雨竹堂浑水摸鱼，打探罗贤图谋桂锡良的阴谋。",
  "dialogues": [
    {
      "speaker": "char_yu_zhu_tang_tu",
      "speaker_name": "雨竹堂徒",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你这两个小喽罗给滚出去，这里没你们说话的馀地。",
      "tone": "厉声",
      "chapter": 73,
      "line_start": 7,
      "line_end": 9
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kou_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "寇仲",
      "listener": "char_gui_xi_liang",
      "text": "桂香主要下属怎样处置这几个胆敢以下犯上的叛徒呢？",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 73,
      "line_start": 27,
      "line_end": 29
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bai_rong",
      "speaker_name": "白荣",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "甚么以下犯上，我白荣乃雨竹堂香主，奉堂主罗贤之命请桂香主去说话，你两个才是以下犯上。",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 73,
      "line_start": 31,
      "line_end": 33
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gui_xi_liang",
      "speaker_name": "桂锡良",
      "listener": "char_bai_rong",
      "text": "请我去说话要动刀子吗？",
      "tone": "沉声",
      "chapter": 73,
      "line_start": 35,
      "line_end": 37
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kou_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "寇仲",
      "listener": "char_bai_rong",
      "text": "这就是白香主不对了。这样吧！我们就把他们缚了去请罗堂主评评理，看看谁对谁错。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 73,
      "line_start": 39,
      "line_end": 43
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kou_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "寇仲",
      "listener": "char_gui_xi_liang",
      "text": "怎么样？要不要去大闹雨竹堂，杀杀罗大堂主的威风。桂香主你若不去，就由我们两个小喽罗代劳。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 73,
      "line_start": 53,
      "line_end": 55
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gui_xi_liang",
      "speaker_name": "桂锡良",
      "listener": "char_kou_zhong",
      "text": "先回军师府再说吧。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 73,
      "line_start": 57,
      "line_end": 59
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mai_yun_fei",
      "speaker_name": "麦云飞",
      "listener": "char_kou_zhong",
      "text": "师傅有命令，由现在起，所有陌生人均不得进入军师府。",
      "tone": "严肃",
      "chapter": 73,
      "line_start": 79,
      "line_end": 81
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gui_xi_liang",
      "speaker_name": "桂锡良",
      "listener": "char_mai_yun_fei",
      "text": "他两个是当年在扬州壮烈牺牲的忠烈士言宽的门生，近年在江湖闯荡，练得一身好武艺，刚才还把雨竹堂的白荣打得落花流水，所以我才希望能向邵军师作推介。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 73,
      "line_start": 83,
      "line_end": 88
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mai_yun_fei",
      "speaker_name": "麦云飞",
      "listener": "char_gui_xi_liang",
      "text": "那要过了今晚才行。",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 73,
      "line_start": 87,
      "line_end": 89
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gui_xi_liang",
      "speaker_name": "桂锡良",
      "listener": "char_kou_zhong",
      "text": "待我先自入府见邵军师，待会再来接你们进府。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 73,
      "line_start": 91,
      "line_end": 93
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xing_rong",
      "speaker_name": "幸容",
      "listener": "char_gui_xi_liang",
      "text": "麦云飞恃着自己是邵军师的大弟子，又得邵兰芳的钟情，一向作威作福，特别排挤我们这批跟随帮主的旧人。迟早我们要使他栽个大斗。",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 73,
      "line_start": 95,
      "line_end": 97
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gui_xi_liang",
      "speaker_name": "桂锡良",
      "listener": "char_xing_rong",
      "text": "不要说废话了，进去再说，你两人记紧在这里等我们。",
      "tone": "沉声",
      "chapter": 73,
      "line_start": 99,
      "line_end": 101
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kou_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "寇仲",
      "listener": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "text": "锡良这混蛋的运道似乎不太好，本有机会飞黄腾达，帮主偏又给昏君宰了。现在更遇上这个处处与他作对的麦云飞，连带两个人入府都给阻头阻势，这种香主还当来作甚么？",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 73,
      "line_start": 105,
      "line_end": 108
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kou_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "寇仲",
      "listener": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "text": "邵兰芳乃我们竹花帮著名的美人儿，不若我们来个横刀夺爱，好气死麦云飞。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 73,
      "line_start": 111,
      "line_end": 113
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "speaker_name": "徐子陵",
      "listener": "char_kou_zhong",
      "text": "若你为这个原因去勾引人家的爱侣，我绝不会容许。",
      "tone": "严肃",
      "chapter": 73,
      "line_start": 115,
      "line_end": 117
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kou_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "寇仲",
      "listener": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "text": "我只是说着玩儿吧！小陵何必那么认真。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 73,
      "line_start": 119,
      "line_end": 121
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kou_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "寇仲",
      "listener": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "text": "锡良身位香主，又是先帮主的关门弟子，地位不低；兼且还有一群先帮主的直属手下支持，你说有没有机会作新帮主呢？否则该不会令麦云飞故意挤压他。",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 73,
      "line_start": 123,
      "line_end": 126
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "speaker_name": "徐子陵",
      "listener": "char_kou_zhong",
      "text": "锡良的道行太浅，怎有资格当帮主。不要扯东道西了，你自己想当帮主才真呢！",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 73,
      "line_start": 127,
      "line_end": 129
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kou_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "寇仲",
      "listener": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "text": "我真的没有此心，亦行不通。现在李密势盛，若我成了竹花帮的龙头，竹花帮可能不到几天就完了。但若锡良成了新帮主，他便只有倚靠我们来支持他，那和我当上帮主没有甚么分别。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 73,
      "line_start": 131,
      "line_end": 135
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "speaker_name": "徐子陵",
      "listener": "char_kou_zhong",
      "text": "你若想锡良当帮主，恐怕要先把帮里现有的甚么军师堂主一股脑儿杀个清光才行，你有那么厉害吗？",
      "tone": "苦笑",
      "chapter": 73,
      "line_start": 137,
      "line_end": 139
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kou_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "寇仲",
      "listener": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "text": "这事确有点困难，却非绝不可能，最重要是锡良乃先帮主的弟子。他这人本来很有胆色，不过可能近来惯于被人欺压，才会失去信心。唔！",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 73,
      "line_start": 141,
      "line_end": 145
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "speaker_name": "徐子陵",
      "listener": "char_kou_zhong",
      "text": "那麦云飞又来了！",
      "tone": "沉声",
      "chapter": 73,
      "line_start": 147,
      "line_end": 148
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kou_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "寇仲",
      "listener": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "text": "该否为锡良出一口气呢？",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 73,
      "line_start": 149,
      "line_end": 151
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mai_yun_fei",
      "speaker_name": "麦云飞",
      "listener": "char_kou_zhong",
      "text": "你这两个小子，这样子在军师府前又坐又卧，成何体统，立即给我滚回所属堂口去。",
      "tone": "厉声",
      "chapter": 73,
      "line_start": 153,
      "line_end": 155
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kou_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "寇仲",
      "listener": "char_mai_yun_fei",
      "text": "麦香主你是否聋了耳朵，听不到桂香主吩咐我们在这里等他吗？你自己滚回去站岗好了。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 73,
      "line_start": 157,
      "line_end": 159
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kou_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "寇仲",
      "listener": "char_mai_yun_fei",
      "text": "怎么？想动手吗？",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 73,
      "line_start": 163,
      "line_end": 164
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mai_yun_fei",
      "speaker_name": "麦云飞",
      "listener": "char_kou_zhong",
      "text": "给我站起来！",
      "tone": "厉声",
      "chapter": 73,
      "line_start": 165,
      "line_end": 166
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kou_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "寇仲",
      "listener": "char_mai_yun_fei",
      "text": "你既非帮主，又非我们的阿爷，凭甚么对我们呼呼喝喝！",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 73,
      "line_start": 167,
      "line_end": 169
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mai_yun_fei",
      "speaker_name": "麦云飞",
      "listener": "char_kou_zhong",
      "text": "掷他们下河！",
      "tone": "厉声",
      "chapter": 73,
      "line_start": 171,
      "line_end": 172
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "speaker_name": "徐子陵",
      "listener": "char_mai_yun_fei",
      "text": "有人来了，你们正事不理，只管欺压自己人，是否有亏职守呢？",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 73,
      "line_start": 195,
      "line_end": 197
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mai_yun_fei",
      "speaker_name": "麦云飞",
      "listener": "char_kou_zhong",
      "text": "迟些再和你们算账。",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 73,
      "line_start": 201,
      "line_end": 202
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kou_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "寇仲",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "世上为何总有这么多爱作威作福的人呢？",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 73,
      "line_start": 205,
      "line_end": 206
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kou_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "寇仲",
      "listener": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "text": "来！让我介绍，这位是宋玉致大小姐。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 73,
      "line_start": 219,
      "line_end": 221
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kou_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "寇仲",
      "listener": "char_song_yu_zhi",
      "text": "我的兄弟徐子陵，长得够英俊吧！",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 73,
      "line_start": 221,
      "line_end": 222
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_song_yu_zhi",
      "speaker_name": "宋玉致",
      "listener": "char_kou_zhong",
      "text": "看在你们尚未有甚么恶行，立即给我离城，否则我只要一句说话，你们休想有命离开。",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 73,
      "line_start": 223,
      "line_end": 225
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kou_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "寇仲",
      "listener": "char_song_yu_zhi",
      "text": "小弟差点忘了我兄弟的人头非常值钱，宋小姐即管大叫大嚷吧！看看我们在被杀前可拉多少人陪葬？",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 73,
      "line_start": 227,
      "line_end": 229
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_song_yu_zhi",
      "speaker_name": "宋玉致",
      "listener": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "text": "劝你的兄弟和你一起走吧！若给人知晓你们在这里，会令你们有天大麻烦的。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 73,
      "line_start": 231,
      "line_end": 233
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "speaker_name": "徐子陵",
      "listener": "char_song_yu_zhi",
      "text": "我们根本不怕任何人，否则就不会在这里与宋小姐说话了。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 73,
      "line_start": 235,
      "line_end": 237
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_song_yu_zhi",
      "speaker_name": "宋玉致",
      "listener": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "text": "你们虽闯出点名堂，但比起李密仍差远了，好好想一想吧！",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 73,
      "line_start": 239,
      "line_end": 241
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kou_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "寇仲",
      "listener": "char_song_yu_zhi",
      "text": "宋小姐是否看上了我这英俊的兄弟，为何对他这么和颜悦色，而对我却声色俱厉。说到底，我和你的感情该深厚点才对。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 73,
      "line_start": 243,
      "line_end": 245
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_song_yu_zhi",
      "speaker_name": "宋玉致",
      "listener": "char_kou_zhong",
      "text": "闭嘴！",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 73,
      "line_start": 247,
      "line_end": 248
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_song_yu_zhi",
      "speaker_name": "宋玉致",
      "listener": "char_kou_zhong",
      "text": "给我站着。",
      "tone": "厉声",
      "chapter": 73,
      "line_start": 251,
      "line_end": 252
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "speaker_name": "徐子陵",
      "listener": "char_kou_zhong",
      "text": "仲少是否想以她来代替李秀宁呢？",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 73,
      "line_start": 267,
      "line_end": 268
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kou_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "寇仲",
      "listener": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "text": "儿女私情，只会增加精神上的负担，我不介意找个美人儿来调剂一下，但却绝不会动情。正事要紧，其他都要摆在一旁。逗逗这高傲的宋家小姐可以，若要劳烦我寇仲去讨好她，奉承她，却是休想。明白吗？",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 73,
      "line_start": 269,
      "line_end": 273
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "speaker_name": "徐子陵",
      "listener": "char_kou_zhong",
      "text": "但现在该怎办呢？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 73,
      "line_start": 275,
      "line_end": 276
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kou_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "寇仲",
      "listener": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "text": "一是立即离开，一是待至今晚大闹他娘的一场。你怎么说？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 73,
      "line_start": 277,
      "line_end": 279
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "speaker_name": "徐子陵",
      "listener": "char_kou_zhong",
      "text": "我建议的你定不同意。照我的想法竹花帮的事我们既管不了亦没有那心力。何况段玉成他们仍在等候我们，多一事不如少一事，我们的烦恼还不够多吗？",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 73,
      "line_start": 281,
      "line_end": 285
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kou_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "寇仲",
      "listener": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "text": "不要对我有那么多偏见好吗？我寇仲甚么时候敢不尊重你陵少的说话。就如你所言，我们偷了骡车就走，两辆都怕够了吧！",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 73,
      "line_start": 287,
      "line_end": 289
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "speaker_name": "徐子陵",
      "listener": "char_kou_zhong",
      "text": "那里有骡车偷？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 73,
      "line_start": 291,
      "line_end": 292
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kou_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "寇仲",
      "listener": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "text": "当然是到风竹堂去偷，他们那么多骡子骡车，借两辆给我们该没有问题，随便找个藉口，就可把骡车骗上手，这可包在我身上。",
      "tone": "得意",
      "chapter": 73,
      "line_start": 293,
      "line_end": 295
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "speaker_name": "徐子陵",
      "listener": "char_kou_zhong",
      "text": "沈北昌和骆奉对我们这么好，怎可以怨报德？",
      "tone": "严肃",
      "chapter": 73,
      "line_start": 297,
      "line_end": 298
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kou_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "寇仲",
      "listener": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "text": "都是你说得对，那就不如到雨竹堂去看看，横竖已结下梁子，差不在再多一项。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 73,
      "line_start": 299,
      "line_end": 301
    },
    {
